<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-advantage-of">take advantage of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>利用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Parents should actively urge their children to take advantage of the opportunity to join sports teams.
父母应积极催促孩子利用这一机会参加运动队。</p><footer>2016 江苏</footer></div></div>